        {
            "title": "英國預算案風向突變 財政大臣考慮放棄增稅計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"英國預算案風向突變 財政大臣考慮放棄增稅計畫\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6tUgnv97CJNC.6U8ovdEBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/a06c7720-b95f-11f0-a777-491225be69e6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">英國預算案風向突變 財政大臣考慮放棄增稅計畫</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E9%A2%A8%E5%90%91%E7%AA%81%E8%AE%8A-%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E5%A2%9E%E7%A8%85%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-005837852.html",
